  "body": "### Description\r\n\r\nAfter merging https://github.com/quarkusio/quarkus/pull/30506 `io.quarkus.maven.it.DevMojoIT.testThatTheApplicationIsReloadedMultiModule` started to fail with the OOME. Although these dev mode tests are run with `-Xmx128m`, they do highlight an issue in the way our config classes are generated currently.\r\n\r\n### Implementation ideas\r\n\r\nAs an alternative to the current impl, @radcortez suggested to switch to the ConfigMapping approach instead in https://quarkusio.zulipchat.com/#narrow/stream/187038-dev/topic/OOME.20in.20main/near/343476381",
